rest_controller_class\";s:24:\"WP_REST_Terms_Controller\";s:13:\"show_tagcloud\";i:1;s:18:\"show_in_quick_edit\";i:1;s:17:\"show_admin_column\";i:0;s:7:\"rewrite\";a:3:{s:17:\"permalink_rewrite\";s:12:\"taxonomy_key\";s:10:\"with_front\";s:1:\"1\";s:20:\"rewrite_hierarchical\";s:1:\"0\";}s:9:\"query_var\";s:13:\"post_type_key\";s:14:\"query_var_name\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"default_term\";a:1:{s:20:\"default_term_enabled\";s:1:\"0\";}s:4:\"sort\";i:0;s:8:\"meta_box\";s:7:\"default\";s:11:\"meta_box_cb\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"meta_box_sanitize_cb\";s:0:\"\";}', 'Head office', 'head-office', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'taxonomy_69c5ec0cafbcc', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:31:53', '2026-03-27 02:31:53', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=acf-taxonomy&#038;p=437', 0, 'acf-taxonomy', '', 0),
(439, 1, '2026-03-27 09:37:10', '2026-03-27 02:37:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>City of Melbourne</strong>&nbsp;is the local government authority for central Melbourne and nearby suburbs, delivering services to residents, businesses, and visitors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>It is Victoria’s cultural, administrative, and recreational hub, known for its vibrant diversity and rich history.<br>The city also leads in urban planning, sustainability, and community engagement initiatives.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'City of Melbourne', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'city-of-melbourne', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:37:10', '2026-03-27 02:37:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=439', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(440, 1, '2026-03-27 09:39:20', '2026-03-27 02:39:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Deakin University offers a personalised experience, enhanced by innovative digital engagement. We lead by creating opportunities to live and work in a connected, evolving world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Deakin University', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'deakin-university', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:39:20', '2026-03-27 02:39:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=440', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(441, 1, '2026-03-27 09:42:12', '2026-03-27 02:42:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Deloitte, we know that the education landscape is evolving at a rapid pace. We partner with governments, employers and educators to respond to and pre-empt the impact of today’s changes, whilst simultaneously looking over the horizon so that we can shape the future education landscape, and the value it will deliver to our students, employers, institutions and system.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www2.deloitte.com/au/en/pages/public-sector/solutions/education-services.html\">Education Services</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Deloitte', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'deloitte', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:42:13', '2026-03-27 02:42:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=441', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(442, 1, '2026-03-27 09:44:48', '2026-03-27 02:44:48', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>EdTechNZ is a member-funded non-profit organisation in New Zealand that promotes, connects and advances educational technology across the country. They serve as the unified voice for EdTech by supporting innovation in learning, facilitating connections between educators and tech leaders, and helping New Zealand’s EdTech sector grow and export globally.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'EdTech New Zealand', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'edtech-new-zealand', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:44:48', '2026-03-27 02:44:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=442', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(443, 1, '2026-03-27 09:47:07', '2026-03-27 02:47:07', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Global Victoria. Take on the world.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We open the world to Victorian businesses, and welcome the business world to Victoria.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Great ideas break boundaries. We believe they should be shared for the world to see. For those who see the bigger picture, we’re here to make global possibilities a reality.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And once you see the world like we do, you’ll be ready to take it on too.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Global Victoria', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'global-victoria', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:34:41', '2026-03-27 03:34:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=443', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(444, 1, '2026-03-27 09:50:36', '2026-03-27 02:50:36', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Inquisitive provides high quality lessons, assessments and teaching tools to 70% of Australian primary schools across Science, History, Geography, Maths and English (Years F-6).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Using a powerful evidence-base, the Inquisitive teaching platform addresses all the dimensions of the Australian Curriculum and state syllabuses, so teachers are fully empowered to lift outcomes and support students.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An independent study by the Centre for Evidence and Implementation (2023/24) and a survey of 1,000 schools, found that Inquisitive delivers a significant increase in teacher wellbeing and saves teachers over 12 days a year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Supported by Save The Children, Inquisitive is focused on equity of learning for all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Inquisitive', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'inquisitive', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:50:37', '2026-03-27 02:50:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=444', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(445, 1, '2026-03-27 09:54:51', '2026-03-27 02:54:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Intellischool is transforming the way educators interact with and learn from data. Our products enable the integration of disparate data sources into a unified data ecosystem.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our clients benefit from numerous automation tools, data cleansing, and insightful, AI-powered visualisations designed to improve both learner outcomes and business efficiency.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Intellischool', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'intellischool', '', '', '2026-03-27 09:58:34', '2026-03-27 02:58:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=445', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(447, 1, '2026-03-27 10:00:26', '2026-03-27 03:00:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Monash University was established in Melbourne, Australia in 1958. We are a youthful organisation, enthusiastic, optimistic and accessible. We believe quality education and research can change the world for the better.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Monash University', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'monash-university', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:00:27', '2026-03-27 03:00:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=447', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2026-03-27 10:02:30', '2026-03-27 03:02:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Open Universities Australia (OUA)</strong>&nbsp;is a trusted not-for-profit online higher-education platform connecting learners with hundreds of subjects and degrees from leading Australian universities</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>OUA provides free, unbiased guidance through dedicated student advisors who help you find the right study path and support you from enrolment to graduation&nbsp;<br>They enable flexible enrolment—even for individual subjects with no prior requirements, making university more accessible and adaptable to your lifestyle<br>With over 30 years of experience and more than 500,000 students empowered, OUA is Australia’s longest‑standing provider of online higher education.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Open Universities Australia', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'open-universities-australia', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:02:30', '2026-03-27 03:02:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=448', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(449, 1, '2026-03-27 10:02:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:02:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&p=449', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(450, 1, '2026-03-27 10:02:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:02:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&p=450', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(451, 1, '2026-03-27 10:05:58', '2026-03-27 03:05:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>StepsWeb is a New Zealand EdTech platform that delivers structured, research-based literacy instruction in reading, spelling, and comprehension. It adapts to each learner’s level with personalized activities, while giving teachers powerful diagnostic tools and progress tracking. Widely used in schools and homes, it supports all learners, including those with dyslexia and other learning needs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Stepsweb', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stepsweb', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:05:59', '2026-03-27 03:05:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=451', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(452, 1, '2026-03-27 10:08:00', '2026-03-27 03:08:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Study Melbourne</strong>&nbsp;is a Victorian Government initiative offering tailored support and resources to international students living and studying in Victoria, Australia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Through the vibrant&nbsp;<strong>Study Melbourne Hub</strong>&nbsp;in central Melbourne, they provide study spaces, free Wi‑Fi, legal and career advice, events, and networking opportunities.&nbsp;<br>They deliver programs like Live (Lead • Intern • Volunteer • Experience) and free professional development, enriching students’ employability and community integration.&nbsp;<br>Study Melbourne also promotes Victoria as a premier destination for global learners, supporting education providers and fostering strong international education partnerships.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Study Melbourne', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'study-melbourne', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:08:00', '2026-03-27 03:08:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=452', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(453, 1, '2026-03-27 10:10:26', '2026-03-27 03:10:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Study NSW leads the NSW Government’s support for international students and the international education sector. We partner with businesses and communities to support international students and promote NSW as the world’s best place to study.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our state offers unparalleled opportunities to learn, work and explore. We are proud to support NSW in providing a globally competitive education in a safe, friendly and welcoming environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Study NSW', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'study-nsw', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:10:26', '2026-03-27 03:10:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=453', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
(454, 1, '2026-03-27 10:13:59', '2026-03-27 03:13:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Toddle is Australia’s fastest-growing LMS and the world’s leading AI-powered teaching and learning platform. Going beyond a typical LMS, Toddle streamlines all aspects of teaching &amp; learning – from curriculum planning and assessments to progress reports and communication.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>More than 2,000 schools across the world trust Toddle to help teachers reclaim valuable time so they can focus on what matters most—teaching.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Toddle', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'toddle', '', '', '2026-03-27 10:14:00', '2026-03-27 03:14:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tienThemes3/?post_type=partner&#038;p=454', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
